        • sibling

          Point sibling
          Every point instance has a sibling in form of an PointType.INNER or PointType.OUTER type.

          The siblings are both displayed on the canvas even though OUTER instances are not visible.

        • type

          PointType type
          The PointType of the point instance.

        • initial_x

          double initial_x
          The initial x coordinate at which the point instance was created via click on the front-end side.

          Necessary to create a constant Point.hashCode() of the point instance.

        • initial_y

          double initial_y
          The initial y coordinate at which the point instance was created via click on the front-end side.

          Necessary to create a constant Point.hashCode() of the point instance.
